{"tid":122834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[特首選戰] 假如林鄭當選，香港玩L完","createTime":"2017-02-16T10:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T00:44:36.000Z","uid":50360,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c20c88e7e0e0a03c11b906a68956aa5daf55516","tid":122834,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:58:32.000Z","msg":"特首選戰提名係2月14日開始，有傳受中聯辦加持嘅林鄭月娥已取得300選委票，比品客只拎得17票多出二百幾票，林鄭形勢絕對大好﹗不過，自林鄭宣佈參選後就關公百出，由選舉口號、拍片到老公給自己的情書，鑊鑊新鮮鑊鑊金，民望被品客遠遠拋離。只可惜係，特首選舉只係1200人小圈子選舉，我同你都冇份投票。<br />\n<br />\n當大家以為品客可與林鄭一戰時，係我剪片個陣，見到知名網絡燈神燒山話自己一定支持品客叔叔果陣，睇嚟大家準備要為香港報喪鳥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RSzZa1SdOvo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRSzZa1SdOvo&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe29ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=860bd036\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RSzZa1SdOvo</a>"},{"pid":"8dc485df82f692c3cdf8e7e131220031bc9799b2","tid":122834,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:02:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce9059604004f36d9529d0038ef2691fdb21a959","tid":122834,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錯!燒山已經買重林鄭會贏<br />\n香港呢次有救</blockquote><br />\n燒山條片名係厄大家<br />\n佢內容講支持品客 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d47bea5d91e2b3016e1697365df4c57ead87fb","tid":122834,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:17:34.000Z","msg":"外省大媽贏梗"},{"pid":"214a1e1a834799722787d13757cf1f0f539f3eb5","tid":122834,"uid":70399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:20:41.000Z","msg":"我地都冇得簡架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4725fdb58512bd0995739dd0d952dce409271e0","tid":122834,"uid":53705,"like":0,